description: Bangfu Technology Group Co., Ltd. does not have significant operations. It intends to develop personal daily life assistance mobile applications, online educational trainings, and employment recruitment services. The company was formerly known as Kelinda, Inc. and changed its name to Bangfu Technology Group Co., Ltd. in June 2020. Bangfu Technology Group Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Liuzhou, the People's Republic of China.
